### Build the windows 50 bed file

source bedtools-2.28.0

bedtools makewindows -g TAIR10_cs.txt -w 50

### Use w50.bed in deeptools multiBigwigSummary; write out result as a .tab for w50 averages

multiBigwigSummary BED-file -b NAME.bw --BED TAIR10_w50.bed -out NAME_w50_multiBigwigSummary.npz --outRawCounts NAME_w50_multiBigwigSummary.tab

